#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:2
msgid "Extending the CLI"
msgstr "扩展 CLI"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:4
msgid "This guide explains how to add new subcommands to the ``lmcache`` CLI."
msgstr "本指南介绍如何为 ``lmcache`` CLI 添加新子命令。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:7
msgid "Architecture Overview"
msgstr "架构概述"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:9
msgid "The CLI uses explicit command registration:"
msgstr "CLI 使用显式命令注册："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:11
msgid "Each command is a class inheriting from ``BaseCommand``."
msgstr "每个命令都是一个继承自 ``BaseCommand`` 的类。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:12
msgid ""
"Commands are instantiated and listed in a central ``ALL_COMMANDS`` "
"registry."
msgstr "所有命令均在中央 ``ALL_COMMANDS`` 注册表中实例化并列出。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:13
msgid ""
"At startup, the entry point iterates ``ALL_COMMANDS`` and calls "
"``cmd.register(subparsers)`` to wire up argparse."
msgstr "启动时，入口点遍历 ``ALL_COMMANDS`` 并调用 ``cmd.register(subparsers)``，将各子命令注册到 argparse。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:16
msgid ""
"``BaseCommand`` is an abstract class with a small set of required methods"
" (name, help, argument registration, and execute). Forgetting any of them"
" raises ``TypeError`` at instantiation time."
msgstr "``BaseCommand`` 是一个抽象类，包含少量必需方法（名称、帮助、参数注册及执行）。若遗漏其中任一方法，实例化时将引发 ``TypeError``。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:21
msgid "Step-by-Step: Adding a New Command"
msgstr "逐步指南：添加新命令"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:23
msgid "**Step 1.** Create a new command class that subclasses ``BaseCommand``:"
msgstr "**步骤 1.** 创建一个继承自 ``BaseCommand`` 的新命令类："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:51
msgid "**Step 2.** Add an instance of it to the ``ALL_COMMANDS`` registry:"
msgstr "**步骤 2.** 将其实例添加到 ``ALL_COMMANDS`` 注册表中："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:62
msgid ""
"That's it --- ``lmcache describe --url http://localhost:8000`` is now "
"available."
msgstr "至此，``lmcache describe --url http://localhost:8000`` 即可正常使用。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:65
msgid "Using the Metrics System"
msgstr "使用指标系统"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:67
msgid "The metrics system uses a **handler + formatter** architecture:"
msgstr "指标系统使用 **处理器 + 格式化器** 架构："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:69
msgid "**Metrics** — the collector. Holds sections and entries."
msgstr "**指标** — 收集器。包含部分和条目。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:70
msgid "**Handler** — the destination (stdout, file, etc.)."
msgstr "**处理器** — 目标（标准输出、文件等）。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:71
msgid "**Formatter** — the rendering (ASCII table, JSON, etc.)."
msgstr "**格式化器** — 渲染（ASCII 表格、JSON 等）。"

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:73
msgid ""
"``BaseCommand.create_metrics()`` sets up default handlers automatically, "
"so command authors just build metrics and call ``emit()``:"
msgstr "``BaseCommand.create_metrics()`` 会自动配置默认处理器，命令开发者只需构建指标数据并调用 ``emit()`` 即可："

#: ../../source/developer_guide/cli.rst:95
msgid ""
"The ``--format`` and ``--output`` flags are added automatically by "
"``BaseCommand.register()`` — subcommands do not need to add them "
"manually."
msgstr "``--format`` 和 ``--output`` 标志由 ``BaseCommand.register()`` 自动添加 — 子命令无需手动添加。"

